title: Ep. 551 - Jethalal And Daya To The Rescue - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal arrives at Jethalal's home for help. Daya suggests him to get married. They all decide to go see a astrologer to know his future.

title: Ep. 552 - A Day With Astrologer - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya and Popatlal ask the astrologer as what needs to be done so that he can get married. The astrologer suggests them to go for a shiv yatra. Popatlal invites the Gokuldham society to accompany them.

title: Ep. 553 - Popatlal Excited For Shivratri - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal is consistently reminding the society of Gokuldham to keep fast the next day and to sleep early. Jethalal's father pokes him for the money he has to keep. Daya prays for Popatlal so that he gets a prospective bride.

title: Ep. 554 - Early To Rise - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone is awaken by 4 in the morning by Popatlal who makes sure nobody is late for the shiv yatra. Jethalal wakes up  and decides to give the money to the respective person. While returning, he gets intoxicated with bhaang.

title: Ep. 555 - Jethalal Intoxicated With Bhaang - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak is stressed as Jethalal is intoxicated and tries to confess his love for Babita. Taarak decides to lock him up in his house and leave for shiv yatra. Daya decides to stay back till Jethalal comes.

title: Ep. 556 - Everyone Looks For Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone assumes Jethalal to be kidnapped as he's gone for a long time. Taarak asks the doctor about how to minimize the effect of 'bhaang'. Jethalal realized how he consumed sweets which turned out to be intoxicated.

title: Ep. 557 - The Shiv Yatra - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak comes up with an idea to help Jethalal. Gokuldham society goes for the shiv yatra. Popatlal does everything according to the ritual and waits for his bride.

title: Ep. 558 - Everything In Place - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Anjali doubts Taarak and enquires of him being restless the other day. Jethalal realises how much he is in love with Daya. He decides to gift her something on the occasion of women's day.

title: Ep. 559 - The Delivery Issue - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal decides to gift a gold biscuit to Daya as she had asked for it once. Baga nags behind Jethalal for the delivery of a LCD TV. Jethalal forgets about the gift that he had kept in his pocket.

title: Ep. 560 - Gokuldham Celebrates Women's Day - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Anjali explains to Bhide why it is important to respect women every day and not only on a single occasion. Daya and Anjali decide to visit parlor, on returning Daya found the gold biscuit Jethalal got. Unaware Daya looks for the owner of the biscuit.

title: Ep. 561 - Sundar Demands A Car From Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal compliments Babita as she is about to leave for some work. Sundar demands a car from Jethalal so that he can travel to Mumbai whenever he wants without spending a penny on cab fare.

title: Ep. 562 - Iyer To Gift Babita A Car - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer plans on surprising Babita with a car but is confused between a first-hand or a second-hand car. He goes to Taarak for advice.

title: Ep. 563 - Babita Is Furious With Iyer's Forgetfulness - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita is furious as she is tired of giving Iyer hints about their upcoming wedding anniversary but he does not seem to realize. She shares her misery with other women in society.

title: Ep. 564 - Babita And Iyer's Wedding Anniversary - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita screams with Joy as Iyer surprises her with a huge flower bouquet early in the morning. She loses her calm when he reveals that his wedding anniversary gift will drive her crazy.

title: Ep. 565 - Jethalal Worries On Missing Sundarlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya asks Jethalal to look for Sundarlal. Baga suggests ideas to find Sundar. Worried Daya decides to leave for Ahmedabad to look for Sundar without informing Jethalal.
